<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Build a Distributed Trace in Lambda and Kinesis on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/unsupported-field-workshops/6-lambda-kinesis/</link><description>Recent content in Build a Distributed Trace in Lambda and Kinesis on Splunk Observability Cloud Workshops</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/unsupported-field-workshops/6-lambda-kinesis/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Setup</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/unsupported-field-workshops/6-lambda-kinesis/1-setup/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/unsupported-field-workshops/6-lambda-kinesis/1-setup/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This lab will make a tracing superhero out of you!&lt;/p&gt;
