&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="callout__body"&gt;&lt;p class="callout__title"&gt;Workshop Question&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Redeploy Lambdas</title><link>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/unsupported-field-workshops/6-lambda-kinesis/5-redeploy-lambdas/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://splunk.github.io/observability-workshop/unsupported-field-workshops/6-lambda-kinesis/5-redeploy-lambdas/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="re-deploy-your-lambdas"&gt;
 &lt;span class="heading-text"&gt;Re-deploy your Lambdas&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;a class="heading-anchor" href="#re-deploy-your-lambdas" aria-label="Permalink" aria-hidden="true"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While remaining in your manual directory, run the following commandd to re-deploy your Lambda Functions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs" data-tabs&gt;
&lt;div class="tabs__list" role="tablist"&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-0" class="tabs__btn is-active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-0" tabindex="0" data-tab-label="Deploy Producer Code"&gt;Deploy Producer Code&lt;/button&gt;&lt;button id="tabs-0-tab-1" class="tabs__btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="tabs-0-panel-1" tabindex="-1" data-tab-label="Expected Output"&gt;Expected Output&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs-0-panel-0" class="tabs__panel is-active" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs-0-tab-0" data-tab-label="Deploy Producer Code"&gt;&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
 &lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;sls deploy -f producer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div id="tabs-0-panel-1" class="tabs__panel" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs-0-tab-1" hidden data-tab-label="Expected Output"&gt;&lt;div class="code-block"&gt;
 &lt;div class="code-block__header"&gt;
 &lt;span class="code-block__file"&gt;&lt;span class="code-block__lang"&gt;text&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;button class="code-block__copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy code to clipboard"&gt;Copy&lt;/button&gt;
 &lt;/div&gt;
