&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Congratuations on finishing the lab. You have seen how we complement auto-instrumentation with manual steps to force &lt;code&gt;Producer&lt;/code&gt; function&amp;rsquo;s context to be sent to &lt;code&gt;Consumer&lt;/code&gt; function via a Record put on a Kinesis stream. This allowed us to build the expected Distributed Trace.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>